spec_data.Name: perl-Module-Extract-Namespaces
spec_data.Description:
This module extracts package declarations from Perl code without running the
code.

It does not extract:

 * Packages declared dynamically (e.g. in eval)
 * Packages created as part of a fully qualified variable name
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:25:55 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Extract the package declarations from a module
